participant for any time or period sec administration the pac or its designee shall control and manage the and administration of this plan and make all and incident thereto sec procedure if you believe that the determination is incorrect in any way you must file written claim with the pac the pac ordinarily will respond to the claim within days of the date on which it is received however if of your benefit and the date on which will begin if your claim is in whole or in part you will be told in writing the specific for the decision and will receive an explanation of the for the decision can also present written which explain why you believe that the benefit should be and may review all pertinent plan generally the decision will be within days after the pac request for reconsideration
